<br>
Are you making sure to get at least a 46 to 48 hitting pet?<br>
<br>
Are you waiting for Fire pet to DS self?<br>
<br>
Are you giving the pet Phantom Plate Armor?<br>
<br>
I just started hunting these myself. I had never been to BG's before. They hit for decent damage, but have very low hp's. <br>
<br>
